{"type": "article", "id": 30571, "title": "越南的这所住宅，在房间的任何角度都可以看到绿色", "description": "“客户想要一个大房子和一个大花园”。", "date": "2016-08-05T05:15:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13896, "name": "越南"}, {"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}, {"id": 26511, "name": "武重义"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 188, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608041054004fqpJLUox1GbcQke.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>在越南推行绿色建筑的武重义最近在芽庄（Nha Trang）做了一个住宅。这里是越南南部的海滨城市，全年气温稳定在 24℃ 到 28℃ 左右，覆盖有大量的植被，是一个舒适悠闲的小城。建筑师拿到了一块占地面积近 500㎡ 的地方，他们得到的诉求是“一个大房子和一个大花园。”</p><p>如果翻看过武重义的<a href=\"http://votrongnghia.com/projects/\" rel=\"nofollow\">项目</a>会发现，几乎全部都与绿色植物有关，或者用竹子这类环保材料建造，或者在屋顶上种上绿植，而这个项目也不例外。因为场地的限制，花园就铺在了屋顶上。不同的是这一带建筑要求使用倾斜的屋顶，武重义他们就用间距较大的台阶代替，种上 4 排绿植，其余地方覆盖上传统的瓦片。从远处望去，屋顶的绿植和周围的树木连在一起，有田园的宁静安逸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105508tTLGal57g9AfM6cO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.347222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105517no23jyM7iWqUVvH6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105517YM7JayGKdwUhoAVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105517eFHa0urZV4NJw1bK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>室内可以平分为两个部分，卧室区域在倾斜屋顶较高的一侧，有上下两层，较低的的一侧只有一层客厅、餐厅、厨房等，因而能获得更高的层高。</p><p class=\"\">绿色植物依然能在房子内部看到，房屋中间有三处小天井，就像一个小的方形庭院，它同样有借光的作用。黑色铁框的玻璃窗是最简单的一种，光线和绿植都可以最大化看到，不会干扰到视线。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804122353N7jvDhKWakqngLyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">在房间任何角度都可以看到绿植。</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804122358Ag9ErhodbeXOZv3q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080412233996eay1L4HunpbhBz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804122351hUOB3cqL2seHPSXT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105552UwkJXQ4KCqtAxZgn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.255342\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105552AyWI5ZsaX4voP3HL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.224359\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105552YtHh7us5V2RLQepk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.282051\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><p>室内外都使用了最简单的白色砖墙，契合乡土的气氛也带给人清爽的审美。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105608GFmyHai0Q8DMNwqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105608f8dMIwg7sG2DTO5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105623UajKHVkc39sY1Aoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105624SWlG1iquxmgzeKMR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783120\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105624UiDFghYA9pwXBqCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783120\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105624EV7cYr1FlTioXdu2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.480769\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804105624PCLgBx8ef4KOVacs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.479701\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/08/02/nha-trang-house-vo-trong-nghia-masaaki-iwamoto-vietnam-stepped-roof-garden/\" rel=\"nofollow\">dezeen</a></p>"}